{"tid":1689631,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"軍政府時代已來臨：抗爭運動需要面對的八個現實","createTime":"2019-11-03T02:29:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T06:50:23.000Z","uid":144125,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"d0df79adfe552b2e63237671034c6702a957ded3","tid":1689631,"uid":144125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T02:29:00.000Z","msg":"1. 警隊不可能崩潰，甚至前線警察的士氣愈來愈好，因為現在獲授權使用的武器、武力都是空前的，這幾個月前，很多警察一生人都開唔到一槍，而家有得打真人版CS，警隊入面本身很多人都愛好射擊，根本就極度享受過程<br />\n<br />\n2. 踏入第5個月，警隊內部也愈來愈堅定，唔好講白警，連半點懷疑都唔會、唔敢有，出街一定係打曱甴，唔係打人。而一張又一張禁制令變相令辱警罪得以落實，警隊高層也開始仿效市民建立黃色經濟圈的做法，所以當警員見到「藍店」被裝修、罷食時，就等如我們見到黃店被針對的感覺一樣，更深化他們對市民的仇恨心理<br />\n<br />\n3. 社會上大部分資本家、財團始終會站在有權者一方，即使有個別地產商撤資、唔買地，對政府的財政影響仍然不太大。反而，由於遊戲規則同裁判都由對家定，例如向食環署屋宇署投訴這招，政府部門必然放生藍店、針對黃店；而黃店更要面對業主加租或停租約的壓力<br />\n<br />\n4. 到底甚麼是「清算警隊」？今時今日在街上，警察得到有史以來最大的權力、來自政府和背後中共的全力支持，即使他日有獨立調查委員會，委員都只由特首委任，到底可以幾獨立？如果下一句的回應是「所以要解散、清算警隊」，但到底民間現在手上爭取到甚麼權力做這件事？<br />\n<br />\n5. 警暴不是香港獨有的問題，幾乎世界上所有地方的警察都會有濫權的情況（所以先有All Cops Are Bastards這句話），而同時這些濫權警察大多數情況下，都得到國家政權的支持，包括民主國家。所以我自己對&laquo;人權法案&raquo;能否發揮效力是有保留的，當然一定好過冇<br />\n<br />\n6. 國際媒體對香港的關注，雖然稍為回落，但仍未至於完全無視，已很難得。不過我們要明白，國際媒體和輿論，不可能維持每日都位處高水<br />\n<br />\n7. 幾可肯定政府已組織秘密警察或政治警察，而接管港台亦勢在必行，廣播處長將再由政務管出任，廢除公共廣播改為類似中央台的喉舌角色；對電視及新聞出版加以限制，日子都不遠了<br />\n<br />\n8. 韓國六月民主運動兩位大學生犧牲前，有更多的烈士在七年前的光州犧牲，軍政府由1961年執政至1987年，中間經歷36年。台灣由1949年起戒嚴至1987年，歷時38年。這兩個國家的戒嚴時期，軍警隨街捉人審問幾日，台灣更設立「特約茶室」軍妓系統，名義上招募女性自願為軍人提供性服務，但逼良為娼、誘拐少女時有發生<br />\n<br />\n想指出這些觀察或史實並非要帶風向，香港市民無論如何都會繼續在街頭抗爭，即使全民三罷有幾難發動，都要嘗試每個可能性。即使對國際游說工作的方向有保留，但絕對信任在那些方面工作的手足，自己就做自己相信要做、最需要做的基層組織部分。這場運動裡，每個人分工不同，大家一直都在自己的崗位裡，不斷發現問題，然後自行檢討和修正，才是令運動能一直走到今日的動力。<br />\n<br />\n我們未來可能一要在一段極長的時間，可能是3年，可能是30年繼續抗爭，可能經歷更多令人痛心的時刻和畫面，可能出入警局和監獄將會成為我們的日常。但即使如此，我們仍要繼續一如以往的抗爭下去，當我們緊緊地擁抱理想，就必然會有面對現實的覺悟。唯有先實現民主改革，才有轉型正義的可能。<br />\n<br />\nSource：<a href=\"https://radicalhk.com/2019/11/03/military-junta/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fradicalhk.com%2F2019%2F11%2F03%2Fmilitary-junta%2F&d=5AUjfk%2BhgFT%2FKzSacqcGpOIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=f0ceb59c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://radicalhk.com/2019/11/03/military-junta/</a>"},{"pid":"5083ddff628a50a1589427b95fff8357966e165a","tid":1689631,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T02:30:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ea462b5d92f5394b3584ebf8083d751c3c76d89","tid":1689631,"uid":1524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T02:30:45.000Z","msg":"唉diu"},{"pid":"78fc48d3275e7342762ca2c8b01b84152defe71c","tid":1689631,"uid":195350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T02:32:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"00e13747451271292628c4085b0ceb51d96daf16","tid":1689631,"uid":241567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T02:34:12.000Z","msg":"的確如此 推比未有心理準備既人睇"},{"pid":"4c1107053c274b10335bf7f873cea73b4e03fe70","tid":1689631,"uid":64884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T02:34:56.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"68a5d7188ea311497beccd3f766214f82fda73aa","tid":1689631,"uid":209516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T02:35:28.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"8d94812ddeb63c7e5f533d4fa793d2b27e7e38cb","tid":1689631,"uid":318339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T02:35:36.000Z","msg":"我都知！但無能力移民！可以點？"},{"pid":"be7362af7551a29fb147f27bcf68f1e021a5e4f3","tid":1689631,"uid":262035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T02:35:55.000Z","msg":"講得好岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f023af52a362eed82e36cf8adb0e033ba30290d","tid":1689631,"uid":209516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T02:36:05.000Z","msg":"但有一息尚存，都要奮戰到底"},{"pid":"082b8cd899d65acd5826c4fc81e87380800884ec","tid":1689631,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T02:36:36.000Z","msg":"唉diu"},{"pid":"1238d2ad1492b6b0858da357e034edbdf4291dc0","tid":1689631,"uid":239250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T02:37:53.000Z","msg":"工會搞掂未"},{"pid":"5078f60721921546099ce1237bd0d66576cd3b73","tid":1689631,"uid":164491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T02:38:50.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"f764fd521d417cba0e9988e385aca52835f7df18","tid":1689631,"uid":261703,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T02:38:58.000Z","msg":"的確，班狗已經係政府最後武器，佢地唔會被清算，反而權力更加大，越權問題更加嚴重。"},{"pid":"07f53b295389bbefd8ef41d37db3b067e11ac2f3","tid":1689631,"uid":237627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T02:40:12.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f73d5b123597db7acc98b96e62718afec30ba68b","tid":1689631,"uid":33579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T02:40:43.000Z","msg":"總知唔可以放棄<br />\n怯 就輸一世 literally <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"148b2c899c51cff442f0354b20a0ae873a3ad694","tid":1689631,"uid":263261,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T02:44:35.000Z","msg":"終於有人肯認清及道出現實<br />\n現實就係咁殘酷<br />\n歷史已經揭示民主運動不是一朝一夕會成功<br />\n講左好多次呢場仗要打好耐<br />\n個個都end game心態"},{"pid":"98cf54f4e58cff01565ffa1e827fa2d702fbdf62","tid":1689631,"uid":92188,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T02:45:24.000Z","msg":"的確係咁，我可能會移民先，大家都諗下後路啦，兄弟"},{"pid":"108e71afc2f3b79df0bd087c9d7f966266a09951","tid":1689631,"uid":266831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T02:45:51.000Z","msg":"搵人做PoPo 滲透佢"},{"pid":"b3e3b9724633f46d013ec938e4da1c93872c3d9d","tid":1689631,"uid":196758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T02:47:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"240a6372bc7e9af6a79545a7267f99725f8c6dfc","tid":1689631,"uid":233909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T02:49:41.000Z","msg":"呢個現實係5個月前已經要有心理準備,即係700萬人唔可能對抗14億既極權,最多可以搞到經濟差,集唔倒資,攬炒"},{"pid":"51495717927eedc0325abf46ca847d02dc99096a","tid":1689631,"uid":321608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T02:55:01.000Z","msg":"香港人唔罷工就死路一條"},{"pid":"fad63521aee737f6896bdb592f5baa9d600814df","tid":1689631,"uid":321684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T03:01:25.000Z","msg":"可以失敗、可以失望，但不能絕望!!<br />\n<br />\n極權政府一定會倒台，呢個係歴史教既事實。<br />\n<br />\n所以，懇求大家，唔好自殺。我地約好左煲底見架!!!"},{"pid":"13489080a0f6e738718b40d9e429d045598d4163","tid":1689631,"uid":137108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T03:10:48.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n大家都要明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fc8b4f30c8a4525b0dc3ffa683eabaa66e557b9","tid":1689631,"uid":281704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T03:13:51.000Z","msg":"P牌幫推禾都快70，希望早見巴絲可在煲底相認，呢個場景能出現係要堅持"}]}